[27/06/2019 03:53:12] <font color="#ffffff">Vale.</font>
[27/06/2019 03:53:13] <font color="#ffffff">Ha ido a descansar</font>
[27/06/2019 03:53:15] <font color="#ffffff">¿De ti?</font>
